snippet.title: Risu - Gameplay (Old-School Survival Horror Game)
snippet.description:
In this Video we are playing a Old-School Style Survival Horror Game Called Risu. Share your thoughts, leave a comment also Subscribe. #Risu #Creepy #OldSchool #IndieHorror

Risu is a story-driven, survival horror adventure game. Her new home hides a dark secret; Risu Ishikawa must traverse, solve, and survive a hellish architectural-maze of endless personal nightmares, but what lies at the center? 
------------------------------------------

PS5 | PS4 PRO
Xbox Series X|S
Capture Card: elgato 4k60 S+ | Live Gamer 4K - GC573

PC Specs:  
CPU: AMD Ryzen 5950X    
Motherboard: Asus Tuf Gaming X570-Pro (Wifi)
Memory: Corsair Vengeance LPX Black 16GB DDR4 
SSD: Samsung SSD 980 EVO NVMe M.2 (500GB)
Graphics card: MSI RTX 3080 Ventus
Operating System: Windows 10 
Monitor: LG 4K 
------------------------------------------
